<section class="rp-page-main rp-page-main--about">
  <div class="rp-shell">
    {%- if show_breadcrumbs -%}
      {% render 'rp-page-breadcrumbs', title: title %}
    {%- endif -%}

    <div class="rp-page-main__hero-media" data-rp-reveal>
      {% render 'rp-founder-photo',
        image: section.settings.founder_image,
        class_name: 'rp-page-main__feature-image rp-page-main__feature-image--collage',
        alt: 'Founder photo collage'
      %}
    </div>

    <div class="rp-page-main__founder-note" data-rp-reveal>
      <p class="rp-section-eyebrow">About us</p>
      <h1 class="rp-section-heading">A note from our founder</h1>

      <div class="rp-page-main__founder-copy rte">
        <p>
          Between trying on outfits for fun, turning the hallway into a catwalk, and having a mum who always made sure I was the best dressed,
          The Re:P Club was built for people who love fashion and want standout, high quality occasion wear without having to break the bank for
          something you&rsquo;ll only wear once.
        </p>
        <p>
          This platform is dedicated to sourcing premium pieces you can rent with confidence, while simplifying the experience of dressing for
          every celebration of love.
        </p>
        <p>
          From timeless classics to statement styles, I really do hope to make you feel confident, comfortable, and beautifully yourself every
          step of the way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rp-page-main__signoff">
        <div class="rp-page-main__signature-stack">
          <img
            class="rp-page-main__signature-xo"
            src="{{ 'rp-signature-xo.png' | asset_url }}"
            alt="xo signature"
            width="664"
            height="376"
            loading="lazy"
          >
          {%- if section.settings.signature_image != blank -%}
            {{
              section.settings.signature_image
              | image_url: width: 1200
              | image_tag:
                class: 'rp-page-main__signature-image',
                loading: 'lazy',
                widths: '320, 520, 760, 1200',
                alt: 'Founder signature'
            }}
          {%- else -%}
            <img
              class="rp-page-main__signature-image"
              src="{{ 'rp-signature-kind.png' | asset_url }}"
              alt="Founder signature"
              width="1019"
              height="245"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rp-page-main__feature-grid rp-page-main__feature-grid--single">
      <div class="rp-page-main__feature-card" data-rp-reveal>
        <p class="rp-page-main__card-label">Why The Re:P Club exists</p>
        <h2>Luxury occasionwear, without the one-wear guilt.</h2>
        <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">
          We curate premium dresses that feel special, photograph beautifully, and arrive with a rental process that is straightforward from
          booking through return.
        </p>
        <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">
          The goal is simple: fewer stressful outfit searches, more memorable event dressing, and pieces that make you feel like yourself on
          your best day.
        </p>
        {%- if page != blank and page.content != blank -%}
          <div class="rp-page-main__feature-extra rte">{{ page.content }}</div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
